name: Keyboards
description: This Keyboard Enthusiast Mystery Box is filled with all sorts of parts, components, and tools that every mechanical keyboard lover will love to use! The Tier 1 box offers items like switch openers, switch lube, switch trays, mousepads, and deskmats. The tier 2 box offers switches, keycaps, custom coiled cables, and more!

name: Dungeons & Dragons
description: Dungeons and Dragons also known as fantasy tabletop role-playing game. You can enjoy it by playing with your friends, add minatures to your collection or simply show off to your friends.

name: Arts & Crafts box

name: Gardening
description: Gardening mystery box! If you are indoor or outdoor plant lover, we have the right plants for you. Our mystery box includes plants for all your garden needs.

name: Books
description: Mystery books box offers literature pieces from writers such as Edgar Allan Poe, James Baldwin, Ernest Hemingway, Friederich Nietzsche and many more.

name: Beer/Wine

You can reward yourself or your family with fine wine from places such as Italy and France or craft beer from Southern Appalachians. If beer and wine is not your 'hobby' then why not make it one? We offer best prices that anyone can afford! Please, choose from any of our prices.
